# Validates inheritance of `js_tsconfig_package_deps` across Bazel packages:
#
#   dir-a/         — has `package.json`, but the directive is set to `disabled`,
#                    so dir-a's own ts_config rule MUST NOT pick up package.json.
#   dir-a/child/   — has the directive set to `enabled`, has no local
#                    package.json, and so MUST pick up dir-a's package.json
#                    (the closest ancestor) into its ts_config rule's deps.
